&#10;3. Propose priorities and sequencing of next steps: The third commitment focuses on determining the priorities and sequence of actions moving forward. This step will help agencies plan their efforts effectively by understanding which areas require immediate attention and how to approach them in a logical order, ensuring that resources are used efficiently and progress is made systematically.">
